8. Public Checkout Responsibilities (Locked)

Public site (Astro + islands) must:
	•	Create order + order items
	•	Select payment method
	•	Display payment instructions (offline)
	•	Initiate Wompi payment when enabled

Public site never changes fulfillment or payment status.

⸻

9. What Is Explicitly Out of Scope (MVP)
	•	Partial refunds
	•	Returns/exchanges
	•	Shipping cost calculation
	•	Tax calculation
	•	Inventory reservations
	•	Delivery tracking

⸻

10. Final Locked Summary
	•	Orders and payments have separate lifecycles
	•	Offline and online payments fully supported
	•	Merchant must CONFIRM orders
	•	READY state is used (no OUT_FOR_DELIVERY)
	•	Cash orders can be fulfilled before payment
	•	Transfers require payment before fulfillment
	•	Full refunds only in MVP
	•	STAFF can refund
	•	All actions audited

This specification is locked and implementation-ready.